(33, 'Addidas Crocks', 'addidas-crocks', 'ADD998', 4, 18, 4, 6, 6, 'Adidas Crocs: Comfort meets style in these lightweight, durable, and \r\nversatile slip-on shoes. Perfect for casual outings, lounging, or \r\noutdoor adventures, they feature Adidas\' signature design with enhanced \r\ncomfort for all-day wear.', 'Introducing the Adidas Crocs, the ultimate fusion of comfort and style. \r\nCrafted with Adidas\' renowned attention to detail, these slip-on shoes \r\noffer a seamless blend of functionality and fashion-forward design. \r\nWhether you\'re running errands, relaxing at home, or exploring the great\r\n outdoors, these Crocs provide unmatched comfort and support. Made from \r\nhigh-quality materials, they are durable enough to withstand everyday \r\nwear and tear while remaining incredibly lightweight. The iconic Adidas \r\nlogo adds a touch of sporty flair to any outfit. Slip into comfort and \r\nelevate your footwear game with Adidas Crocs.', '<ul><li>Lightweight and durable construction</li><li>Slip-on design for easy wearability</li><li>Enhanced comfort for all-day wear</li><li>Iconic Adidas logo detailing</li><li>Available in a variety of sizes and colors</li></ul>', 0, 0, 1, '2024-03-20 05:43:32', '2024-03-20 05:45:15', 'Shipping: We offer fast and reliable shipping options to ensure your \r\nAdidas Crocs are delivered to your doorstep promptly. Shipping costs and\r\n delivery times may vary based on your location.\r\nReturns: If for any reason you\'re not completely satisfied with your \r\nAdidas Crocs, we offer a hassle-free returns process. Simply return the \r\nunworn shoes in their original packaging within [insert number] days of \r\npurchase for a full refund or exchange. Please refer to our returns \r\npolicy for more details.'),
(34, 'Balenciaga Pushin Slides', 'balenciaga-pushin-slides', 'BAL867', 4, 18, 4, 8, 7.74, 'Balenciaga Pushin Slides: Elevate your casual footwear collection with \r\nthese luxurious slides from Balenciaga. Featuring a sleek design with \r\nthe iconic Balenciaga logo, these slides offer comfort and style for \r\neveryday wear.', 'Step into luxury with the Balenciaga Pushin Slides. Crafted with \r\nmeticulous attention to detail, these slides boast a minimalist yet \r\nsophisticated design that effortlessly enhances any casual ensemble. The\r\n sleek silhouette is complemented by the embossed Balenciaga logo, \r\nadding a touch of designer flair to your look. Whether you\'re lounging \r\npoolside, running errands, or meeting friends for brunch, these slides \r\nprovide unmatched comfort and style. Slip them on and experience the \r\nepitome of effortless chic with Balenciaga Pushin Slides.', '<ul><li>Made from high-quality materials for durability and comfort</li><li>Embossed Balenciaga logo detailing</li><li>Available in a range of sizes and colors to suit your personal style</li><li>Perfect for casual outings, beach days, or relaxing at home</li></ul>', 0, 0, 1, '2024-03-20 05:46:43', '2024-03-20 05:48:56', 'Shipping: Enjoy fast and secure shipping options to ensure your \r\nBalenciaga Pushin Slides arrive promptly. Shipping costs and delivery \r\ntimes may vary depending on your location.\r\nReturns: Your satisfaction is our top priority. If you\'re not completely\r\n satisfied with your Balenciaga Pushin Slides, you can return them \r\nwithin [insert number] days of purchase for a full refund or exchange. \r\nPlease refer to our returns policy for more information.'),
