(37, 'Crocs Crocband', 'crocs-crocband', 'CRO711', 4, 18, 4, 10, 9.55, 'Crocs Crocband: Experience the perfect blend of comfort and style with \r\nCrocs\' iconic Crocband design. These versatile clogs feature a sporty \r\naesthetic and signature Croslite foam construction for all-day comfort.', 'Introducing the Crocs Crocband, the ultimate fusion of comfort and \r\nfashion-forward design. These iconic clogs from Crocs combine a sporty \r\naesthetic with the brand\'s signature comfort features. Crafted from \r\nlightweight and durable Croslite foam material, these clogs are perfect\r\n for everyday wear. The bold stripe detailing and contrasting heel strap\r\n add a touch of retro flair to your look, while the ventilated design \r\nensures breathability and keeps your feet feeling cool and comfortable. \r\nWhether you\'re running errands, relaxing at home, or exploring the \r\noutdoors, the Crocs Crocband offers unmatched comfort and style.', '<ul><li>Made from Crocs\' signature Croslite foam material for lightweight comfort</li><li>Sporty stripe detailing and contrasting heel strap for a stylish look</li><li>Ventilated design for breathability</li><li>Available in a wide range of colors and sizes to suit your personal style</li></ul>', 0, 0, 1, '2024-03-20 06:08:20', '2024-03-20 06:10:24', 'Shipping: Enjoy fast and reliable shipping options to ensure your Crocs \r\nCrocband clogs arrive promptly. Shipping costs and delivery times may \r\nvary based on your location.\r\nReturns: We want you to love your Crocs Crocband clogs. If for any \r\nreason you\'re not completely satisfied, you can return them within 7 days of purchase for a full refund or exchange. Please \r\nrefer to our returns policy for more details.'),
