(40, 'Crocs All-Terrain Atlas Clogs Bone Limeade Unisex Slip On Sandals M 10 W 12', 'crocs-all-terrain-atlas-clogs-bone-limeade-unisex-slip-on-sandals-m-10-w-12', 'CRO831', 4, 18, 4, 19, 18.07, 'Conquer any terrain with confidence in our Crocs All-Terrain Atlas \r\nClogs. Featuring a bold Bone Limeade colorway, these slip-on sandals \r\noffer unrivaled comfort and versatility for both men and women.', 'Gear up for adventure with our Crocs All-Terrain Atlas Clogs in Bone \r\nLimeade. Engineered for versatility and durability, these slip-on \r\nsandals are perfect for outdoor explorations and everyday wear. The \r\nrugged outsole with aggressive tread patterns provides exceptional \r\ntraction on various surfaces, while the lightweight construction ensures\r\n all-day comfort. With a roomy fit and adjustable heel strap, these \r\nclogs offer a secure and customizable fit for both men and women. \r\nWhether you\'re hiking rugged trails, navigating city streets, or \r\nlounging by the pool, the Crocs All-Terrain Atlas Clogs are your go-to \r\nfootwear choice.', '<ul><li>Unisex design suitable for both men and women.</li><li>Ventilation ports for enhanced breathability and quick drying.</li><li>Iconic Crocs Comfort provides superior cushioning and support.</li><li>Easy to clean and maintain, making them ideal for outdoor adventures.</li><li>Bold Bone Limeade colorway adds a pop of style to any outfit.</li></ul>', 0, 0, 1, '2024-03-20 06:31:15', '2024-03-20 06:33:10', 'Experience swift and reliable shipping for your Crocs All-Terrain Atlas \r\nClogs. If you\'re not completely satisfied with your purchase, we offer \r\nhassle-free returns and exchanges to ensure your satisfaction. Our \r\ndedicated customer service team is available to assist you with any \r\ninquiries or concerns.'),
