(43, 'Bahamas Slippers', 'bahamas-slippers', 'BAH121', 4, 18, 4, 8, 7.74, 'Indulge in island-inspired comfort with our Bahamas Slippers. These \r\nstylish and cozy slippers are perfect for lounging at home or strolling \r\nalong sandy shores.', 'Transport yourself to paradise with our Bahamas Slippers. Crafted with \r\nsoft and plush materials, these slippers offer luxurious comfort with \r\nevery step. The vibrant tropical designs and colors evoke the spirit of \r\nthe Bahamas, adding a touch of island flair to your everyday routine. \r\nThe durable outsole provides traction and support, whether you\'re \r\npadding around the house or enjoying a leisurely walk on the beach. Slip\r\n into relaxation mode and let the Bahamas Slippers take you on a journey\r\n to serenity and style.', '<ul><li>Available in a range of sizes to fit men, women, and children.</li><li>Features cushioned footbeds for extra comfort and support.</li><li>Lightweight and easy to pack, making them perfect for travel or gifting.</li><li>Designed with quality materials for long-lasting durability.</li><li>Suitable for indoor and outdoor use, offering versatility for any occasion.</li></ul>', 0, 0, 1, '2024-03-20 06:47:40', '2024-03-20 06:49:19', 'Experience fast and convenient shipping for your Bahamas Slippers. If \r\nyou\'re not completely satisfied with your purchase, we offer hassle-free\r\n returns and exchanges to ensure your satisfaction. Our dedicated \r\ncustomer service team is here to assist you with any questions or \r\nconcerns you may have about your order.'),
